# use cron to run specific tasks following schedule.

#crontab -l will allow us to view crontab entries of current users

# for example

# 0 2 * * * /bin/sh backup.sh

# Our databasewill be backedup at 2am daily,  * * * for all matching records

#Another example

# 0 5,17 * * * /scripts/script.sh

# At 5am and 5pm daily, separated by commas, will be executed.

